<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Registraté</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css" />
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('navbar') %>

    <div class="container-fluid blanco">
      <br />

      <br />

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-5">
          <h2>Registrate como diseñador</h2>
          <form
            action="/designer/register"
            method="post"
            enctype="multipart/form-data"
          >
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="exampleFormControlInput" class="form-label"
                >Nombre</label
              >
              <input
                type="text"
                class="form-control"
                id="exampleFormControlInput"
                name="name"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="exampleFormControlInput3" class="form-label"
                >Apellidos</label
              >
              <input
                type="text"
                class="form-control"
                id="exampleFormControlInput3"
                name="last_name"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="exampleFormControlInput4" class="form-label"
                >Email</label
              >
              <input
                type="email"
                class="form-control"
                id="exampleFormControlInput4"
                placeholder="name@example.com"
                name="email"
              />
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="exampleFormControlInput5" class="form-label"
                >Número de teléfono</label
              >
              <input
                type="text"
                class="form-control"
                id="exampleFormControlInput5"
                name="phone_number"
              />
            </div>

            <div class="mb-3 row">
              <label for="inputPassword" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label"
                >Password</label
              >
              <div class="col-sm-10">
                <input
                  type="password"
                  class="form-control"
                  id="inputPassword"
                  name="password"
                />
              </div>
              <br />
              <br />
              <div class="mb-3">
                <label for="exampleFormControlInput2" class="form-label"
                  >Descripción</label
                >
                <textarea
                  name="description"
                  id="exampleFormControlInput2"
                  class="form-control"
                  cols="30"
                  rows="10"
                ></textarea>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="mb-3">
              <label for="formFile" class="form-label">Imagen de perfil</label>
              <input
                class="form-control"
                type="file"
                id="formFile"
                name="img"
              />
            </div>
            <button class="btn boton2" type="submit">Registrate</button>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="col-xs-12 col-lg-7 union">
          <h2>Ventajas de unirte a ARRECIFE STYLE</h2>
          <br />

          <p>
            Trae tu colección a ARRECIFE STYLE, y aprovecha las numerosas
            ventajas que te brindamos como diseñador emergente. Nuestro
            compromiso hacía los nuevos diseñadores nos desmarca como una
            plataforma de primer orden en la promoción de la moda.
          </p>
          <br />
          <div>
            <img
              src="https://es.habcdn.com/photos/project/big/decoracion-y-diseno-tienda-ropa-ibiza-1768769.jpg"
              alt=""
              style="width: 95%"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br />
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-12">
          <footer class="bg-dark text-center text-white">
            <div class="container p-4 pb-0">
              <section class="foot mb-4">
                <a class="btn-floating m-1" href="#" role="button"
                  ><img
                    src="/images/iconos/facebook.png"
                    style="width: 5vh"
                    alt="" /><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i
                ></a>

                <!-- Twitter -->
                <a class="btn-floating m-1" href="#!" role="button"
                  ><img
                    src="/images/iconos/gorjeo.png"
                    style="width: 5vh"
                    alt="" /><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i
                ></a>

                <!-- Google -->
                <a class="btn-floating m-1" href="#!" role="button">
                  <img
                    src="/images/iconos/instagram.png"
                    style="width: 5vh"
                    alt="" />
                  <i class="fab fa-google"></i
                ></a>

                <!-- Instagram -->
                <a class="btn-floating m-1" href="#!" role="button">
                  <img
                    src="/images/iconos/whatsapp.png"
                    style="width: 5vh"
                    alt="" />
                  <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i
                ></a>
              </section>
              <!-- Section: Social media -->
            </div>
            <!-- Grid container -->

            <div
              class="text-center p-3"
              style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)"
            >
              © 2022 Copyright:
              <a class="text-white" href="https://mdbootstrap.com/"
                >arrecifistyle.es</a
              >
            </div>
          </footer>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
